huion-keydial-mini-driver (1.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Change 'reset' command to clear runtime bindings instead of writing to config file
  * Fix compatibility with read-only filesystems (e.g., NixOS home-manager)
  * Simplify device connection handling and remove unused code
  * Remove auto_reconnect config option (connection handling is core functionality)
  * Handle BlueZ "Notify acquired" errors gracefully
  * Fix reconnection when device powers off from inactivity

 -- JD Flamm <judsonwebdesign@gmail.com>  Wed, 13 May 2026 16:58:00 -0600

